<c.bg_transparent>Todos los nobles están al sol.</c.bg_transparent>

108
00:07:30.375 --> 00:07:32.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Bebiendo, divirtiéndose,</c.bg_transparent>

109
00:07:32.750 --> 00:07:35.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>reverenciando a un sogún</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>que pronto morirá.</c.bg_transparent>

110
00:07:37.583 --> 00:07:38.500 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Deberías comer.</c.bg_transparent>

111
00:07:40.708 --> 00:07:42.458 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Es un día importante.</c.bg_transparent>

112
00:07:47.708 --> 00:07:50.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Solías mirarme con admiración.</c.bg_transparent>

113
00:07:51.416 --> 00:07:53.500 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Planeas matar a mi esposo.</c.bg_transparent>

114
00:07:53.583 --> 00:07:56.250 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Te refieres a la bestia de la que huiste?</c.bg_transparent>

115
00:07:57.083 --> 00:08:01.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Aún no lo entiendes.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Te estoy dando todo lo que quieras.</c.bg_transparent>

116
00:08:01.500 --> 00:08:04.625 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Cuando el sogún</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>y sus partidarios mueran, serás libre.</c.bg_transparent>

117
00:08:04.708 --> 00:08:05.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Una vez que tú,</c.bg_transparent>

118
00:08:06.583 --> 00:08:09.166 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>la única sobreviviente del Clan Itoh,</c.bg_transparent>

119
00:08:09.250 --> 00:08:12.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>declares que apoyas a tu padre</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>como nuevo sogún.</c.bg_transparent>

120
00:08:14.416 --> 00:08:15.333 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No lo haré.</c.bg_transparent>

121
00:08:16.500 --> 00:08:19.708 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Respiraste por primera vez gracias a mí.</c.bg_transparent>

122
00:08:20.291 --> 00:08:23.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Y respiras ahora porque yo te lo permito.</c.bg_transparent>

123
00:08:26.166 --> 00:08:28.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Necesito un hijo.</c.bg_transparent>

124
00:08:28.125 --> 00:08:31.250 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Por una vez en mi vida,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>le pido ayuda a mi hija.</c.bg_transparent>

125
00:08:32.708 --> 00:08:34.375 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ese cerdo blanco y gordo</c.bg_transparent>

126
00:08:34.458 --> 00:08:37.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>cree que seré su títere complaciente.</c.bg_transparent>

127
00:08:37.958 --> 00:08:41.250 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Cuando me deshaga de él,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>todo Japón será mío para…</c.bg_transparent>

128
00:08:49.166 --> 00:08:50.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Seki!</c.bg_transparent>

129
00:08:50.583 --> 00:08:52.083 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Qué está pasando?</c.bg_transparent>

130
00:08:52.166 --> 00:08:53.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Akemi vendrá conmigo…</c.bg_transparent>

131
00:08:55.375 --> 00:08:56.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>si lo desea.</c.bg_transparent>

132
00:08:57.625 --> 00:08:58.500 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tú…</c.bg_transparent>

133
00:08:59.250 --> 00:09:00.458 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Regresaste por mí.</c.bg_transparent>

134
00:09:06.541 --> 00:09:11.500 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hice lo que juzgué mejor para ti,</c.bg_transparent>
