135
00:09:13.625 --> 00:09:15.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Puedes perdonarme, niña?</c.bg_transparent>

136
00:09:17.750 --> 00:09:20.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Todos estos años a mi lado,</c.bg_transparent>

137
00:09:20.125 --> 00:09:22.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>y decides tirar tu vida a la basura hoy,</c.bg_transparent>

138
00:09:23.375 --> 00:09:24.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>por una hija.</c.bg_transparent>

139
00:09:30.666 --> 00:09:32.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Estás respirando</c.bg_transparent>

140
00:09:33.041 --> 00:09:34.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>porque yo te lo permito.</c.bg_transparent>

141
00:09:43.125 --> 00:09:45.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Atrápenlos!</c.bg_transparent>

142
00:09:55.666 --> 00:09:57.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Quién liberó a Lady Akemi?</c.bg_transparent>

143
00:09:58.041 --> 00:10:01.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>A un lado, tonto.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Sabes que represento a Daichi.</c.bg_transparent>

144
00:10:02.083 --> 00:10:03.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No esta vez.</c.bg_transparent>

145
00:10:03.583 --> 00:10:04.625 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Regresen.</c.bg_transparent>

146
00:10:04.708 --> 00:10:05.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Vuelvan a la celda.</c.bg_transparent>

147
00:10:27.250 --> 00:10:28.625 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Quién es tu amigo?</c.bg_transparent>

148
00:10:28.708 --> 00:10:30.333 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No es mi amigo.</c.bg_transparent>

149
00:10:30.833 --> 00:10:33.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Aún quieres tu libertad?</c.bg_transparent>

150
00:10:37.166 --> 00:10:40.791 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Entonces sígueme.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Ringo te espera en la alcantarilla.</c.bg_transparent>

151
00:10:42.625 --> 00:10:43.708 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Ringo?</c.bg_transparent>

152
00:10:44.375 --> 00:10:46.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Tu plan de escape es Ringo?</c.bg_transparent>

153
00:11:10.666 --> 00:11:11.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Funcionó!</c.bg_transparent>

154
00:11:12.166 --> 00:11:13.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Perdón.</c.bg_transparent>

155
00:11:16.791 --> 00:11:19.625 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>La Zambullida del Halcón. Nada mal.</c.bg_transparent>

156
00:11:20.958 --> 00:11:22.250 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Estuviste entrenando.</c.bg_transparent>

157
00:11:23.000 --> 00:11:24.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Taigen! ¡Estás aquí!</c.bg_transparent>

158
00:11:25.500 --> 00:11:26.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>El sogún corre peligro.</c.bg_transparent>

159
00:11:27.583 --> 00:11:32.083 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Aún soy un samurái leal. Vine a advertirle</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>de los insurgentes de Fowler.</c.bg_transparent>

160
00:11:33.416 --> 00:11:34.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Conoces al sogún?</c.bg_transparent>

161
00:11:35.958 --> 00:11:37.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No puedo acercarme a él.</c.bg_transparent>

162
00:11:38.250 --> 00:11:42.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Le dije al guardia en jefe: "El ejército</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>del hombre blanco se acerca a Edo".</c.bg_transparent>

163
00:11:42.750 --> 00:11:45.458 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Me contestó:</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>"No hay hombres blancos en Japón".</c.bg_transparent>

164
00:11:46.625 --> 00:11:50.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>- ¿Dónde está el sogún ahora?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>- En el jardín del castillo, custodiado.</c.bg_transparent>

165
00:11:50.958 --> 00:11:54.375 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Si tratara de llegar a él solo,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>moriría a los siete pasos.</c.bg_transparent>

166
00:11:56.833 --> 00:12:00.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Quizás juntos podamos acercarnos</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>para advertirle antes de morir.</c.bg_transparent>

167
00:12:02.458 --> 00:12:04.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>- Ven y…</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>- El maestro dijo…</c.bg_transparent>

168
00:12:04.083 --> 00:12:08.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Mizu solo piensa en sí mismo</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>y en su venganza.</c.bg_transparent>

169
00:12:09.375 --> 00:12:12.375 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ringo, ¿no dijiste</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>que aspirabas a la grandeza?</c.bg_transparent>

170
00:12:13.666 --> 00:12:16.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Los dioses te están dando esa oportunidad.</c.bg_transparent>

171
00:12:16.500 --> 00:12:21.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ahora, ¿qué haces cuando obtienes</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>exactamente aquello por lo que rezaste?</c.bg_transparent>

172
00:12:24.625 --> 00:12:26.333 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Allí, junto al agua.</c.bg_transparent>

173
00:12:28.125 --> 00:12:29.791 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ocho guardias, arqueros.</c.bg_transparent>

174
00:12:30.375 --> 00:12:31.833 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Cómo los sorteamos?</c.bg_transparent>

175
00:12:32.416 --> 00:12:33.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Un rompecabezas.</c.bg_transparent>

176
00:12:36.125 --> 00:12:37.833 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Qué haría el maestro?</c.bg_transparent>

177
00:12:37.916 --> 00:12:38.833 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Mizu?</c.bg_transparent>

178
00:12:39.333 --> 00:12:42.166 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Mizu es la persona menos cautelosa,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>menos táctica</c.bg_transparent>

179
00:12:42.250 --> 00:12:44.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>y más exasperante que he conocido.</c.bg_transparent>

180
00:12:44.958 --> 00:12:45.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sí.</c.bg_transparent>

181
00:12:47.500 --> 00:12:49.250 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Pero qué haría?</c.bg_transparent>

182
00:12:49.333 --> 00:12:52.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Es tan estúpido</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>que entraría por la puerta principal.</c.bg_transparent>

183
00:13:13.666 --> 00:13:15.458 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>- ¡Alto!</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>- ¡Detengan a los dos!</c.bg_transparent>

184
00:13:16.916 --> 00:13:17.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡No nos ataquen!</c.bg_transparent>

185
00:13:18.000 --> 00:13:20.833 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Escuchen! ¡Venimos a advertirles algo!</c.bg_transparent>

186
00:13:20.916 --> 00:13:22.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Escúchenme!</c.bg_transparent>

187
00:13:22.791 --> 00:13:23.833 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Todo salió bien.</c.bg_transparent>

188
00:13:24.333 --> 00:13:27.625 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Es una criatura odiosa,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>peor aún que los otros blancos.</c.bg_transparent>

189
00:13:30.166 --> 00:13:31.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Taigen!</c.bg_transparent>

190
00:13:35.541 --> 00:13:37.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Por qué haces negocios con él?</c.bg_transparent>

191
00:13:37.750 --> 00:13:38.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Por favor.</c.bg_transparent>

192
00:13:39.708 --> 00:13:42.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Es un lindo día, hablemos de temas lindos.</c.bg_transparent>

193
00:13:42.708 --> 00:13:46.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Takayoshi, ¿dónde está tu flamante esposa?</c.bg_transparent>

194
00:13:46.125 --> 00:13:48.333 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Ya la dejaste exhausta?</c.bg_transparent>

195
00:13:51.375 --> 00:13:55.166 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Mátenme si quieren!</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>¡Pero déjenme advertirle algo al sogún!</c.bg_transparent>

196
00:13:55.750 --> 00:13:57.625 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Su vida corre peligro!</c.bg_transparent>

197
00:14:05.916 --> 00:14:06.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿El sogún?</c.bg_transparent>

198
00:14:07.625 --> 00:14:10.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Quién osa apuntar su arma</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>hacia al sogún?</c.bg_transparent>

199
00:14:10.291 --> 00:14:11.708 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No soy un asesino.</c.bg_transparent>

200
00:14:12.333 --> 00:14:16.125 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Soy un leal samurái de Kioto,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>sirvo a Daichi Tokunobu.</c.bg_transparent>

201
00:14:16.208 --> 00:14:18.708 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Vine a intentar evitar que maten al sogún.</c.bg_transparent>

202
00:14:20.291 --> 00:14:23.500 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Abijah Fowler se aproxima</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>con un ejército</c.bg_transparent>

203
00:14:24.375 --> 00:14:25.791 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>armado con fusiles.</c.bg_transparent>

204
00:14:26.458 --> 00:14:27.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Por favor,</c.bg_transparent>

205
00:14:28.208 --> 00:14:29.166 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>solo mírame,</c.bg_transparent>

206
00:14:30.250 --> 00:14:31.250 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>y luego mátame.</c.bg_transparent>

207
00:15:19.375 --> 00:15:23.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Cierren todas las puertas!</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>¡Se aproxima el ejército!</c.bg_transparent>

208
00:15:23.500 --> 00:15:25.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Date prisa. No tenemos mucho tiempo.</c.bg_transparent>

209
00:15:28.666 --> 00:15:29.500 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Esperen.</c.bg_transparent>

210
00:15:33.541 --> 00:15:35.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Por qué nos detenemos?</c.bg_transparent>

211
00:15:37.083 --> 00:15:38.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Libertad.</c.bg_transparent>

212
00:15:39.125 --> 00:15:42.250 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Recuperé una parte de tu dote.</c.bg_transparent>

213
00:15:42.333 --> 00:15:46.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Con esto, puedes ir a cualquier parte.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Vivir la vida que quieras.</c.bg_transparent>

214
00:15:46.500 --> 00:15:48.791 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
